These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, havana
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, january
1. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Cigar           | havana | ritmeester |
| Birthday   | january     | august  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, italian
2 different games are played: whist, billiard
1. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Nationality         | italian   | egyptian      |
| Game   | whist | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, mechanic
2 different games are played: chess, backgammon
1. the electrician is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Job   | mechanic | electrician    |
| Game     | chess | backgammon |

 #################################

 
